    "body": "Lighthouse also doesn’t follow [the Prometheus convention to namespace metrics](https://prometheus.io/docs/practices/naming/#metric-names). There might be two applications monitored by the same Prometheus instance that have a metric like `async_tasks_count`, and we wouldn’t be able to tell them apart easily. Therefore the recommendation is to add the name of the application as prefix, e.g. `lighthouse_async_tasks_count`.",
